      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The old snowpack will be prone to triggering in some places. Towards its base, the snowpack is faceted and weak. This applies in particular on steep shady slopes above approximately 2000 m. Remotely triggered avalanches are possible in isolated cases. <br/> Towards its surface, the snowpack is unfavourably layered and its surface has a melt-freeze crust that is barely capable of bearing a load."
      },
